import{Card, Button, Col} from 'react-bootstrap'
import shortenText from '../../shared/utils'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

const PhoneDetailsCard = ({name, manufacturer, description, color, price, screen,  imageFileName, _id}) => {

    return(
        <Col md={4}>
        <Card >
            <Card.Img variant="top" src={imageFileName} />
            <Card.Body>
                <Card.Title>{name}</Card.Title>
                <Card.Subtitle>{}</Card.Subtitle>
                <Card.Text>{shortenText(description, 70)}</Card.Text>
                <Link to = {`phones/phone/${_id}`} >
                    <Button variant="primary">Try Me!</Button>
                </Link>
            </Card.Body>
        </Card>
        </Col>
    )
}

export default PhoneDetailsCard
